Feature : Create account
As a new customer 
I want to create my account
In order to become client of the bank

Scenario:
Given a new user "coucou@gmail.com"
When "coucou@gmail.com" creates an account
Then account is created with a balance 0.

Feature: Check balance
As a new customer
I want to check my balance
In order to manager my account

Scenario: 
Given a new user "maria.frih"
When "maria.frih" accesses her account for the first time
Then the balance is 0 euros

